      {
        name: "Polio Vaccination Drives",
        location: "Antop Hill",
        description: "The Polio Vaccination Drives at Antop Hill aim to eradicate polio through community-wide vaccination efforts. Volunteers work tirelessly to vaccinate the children, protecting them from the effects of polio and promoting public health."
